    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps with Argand burners and ring-shaped reservoirs of wedge-shaped cross section designed to cast as little shadow as possible.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
